OL,3,CJapanese people to all have same
OL,4,Csurname by 2531, study shows
OL,6,Fpeople will all have the same surname
OL,7,Fby the year 2531 because of the
OL,8,Fcountry's laws around marriage, a new
OL,9,Fstudy has revealed.
OL,11,FProfessor Hiroshi Yoshida of Tohoku
OL,12,FUniversity's Center for Research on
OL,13,FAging, Economy and Society projected
OL,14,Fthat current Japanese marriage laws
OL,15,Fwill mean every citizen will be known
OL,16,Fas 'Sato-san' in just over 500 years.
