OL,3,CJapanese people to all have same
OL,4,Csurname by 2531, study shows
OL,6,FIf the rate remains the same, around
OL,7,Fhalf of Japan's population will take
OL,8,Fthe surname by 2446 and all will have
OL,9,Fit by 2531.
OL,11,FProf Yoshida's calculations were made
OL,12,Fby analysing the population growth
OL,13,Frate and demographic trends of the
OL,14,Fsurname "Sato", but conceded he made
OL,15,Fseveral assumptions which caused
OL,16,Flimitations to the research.
