OL,3,CJapanese people to all have same
OL,4,Csurname by 2531, study shows
OL,6,FMany women, gender equality experts,
OL,7,Fand even a United Nations committee
OL,8,Fhave called these laws outdated and
OL,9,Fcalled for change.
OL,11,FOver the years, several couples who
OL,12,Fwanted to keep their own names have
OL,13,Fgone to the Japanese Supreme Court to
OL,14,Fchallenge the law but all have been
OL,15,Fdismissed.
